channel.title: Looking for dev's for rs06 server
channel.description:
hey guys, im thinking of starting a rs06 remake server. as ive seen in other 06 remakes, the devs are too money hungry and just stop developing once their server grows big.
anyways im looking for skilled dev's to help me with this.
note: im not a very good coder myself, i know some, but not all. i can provide a website and host while we get it running, also i can advertise the server.
if your interested to talk about it add my skype : projectrs.gold1 thanks :D
